title: Crumpled City Chicago Map
description:
Lightweight, durable, soft and waterproof, this map can be shoved in a pocket, crumpled into a ball and repacked over and over again. 

Each Map Includes:

  • Details about a large part of the city, including streets, monuments, museums, art galleries and much more.
  • Soulsights, which are unique places specifically chosen to move, touch and inspire the modern traveler.
  • Map measures 34.25 in. x 22.8 in.
  • Made in Italy
